%8Dc/author-GeG00MtiZbanyzO5k2cQ-g">Khâu Trung Ngọc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/N%C3%B4ng-gia-%C6%B0u-t%C6%B0/poem-hwziF0-W90LE6l0TQKk9nQ">Nông gia ưu tư - 農家憂思</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%81n/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-L%E1%BB%99-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-hi%E1%BB%87u-K%E1%BB%B3-Am/poem-CIy274HeMPfIg076gKBn6g">Tặng Nguyễn Lộ Trạch (hiệu Kỳ Am) - 贈阮露澤（號琦菴）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-k7nDOMHcGKaZoky6ue8-ag">Nguyễn Thượng Hiền</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87n-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-s%C6%B0/Tu-T%C3%A2y-ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BB%9Di/poem-GRNH9SS7MhDNhNNF3-MOJQ">Tu Tây phương thập nhị thời - 修西方十二時</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87n-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-s%C6%B0/author-D3nlI_QzeVjknjQ7vGsW3w">Thiện Đạo đại sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%C3%A3-%C4%90%C3%A1i/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-t%C3%A1i-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-oW3GkPhZOH2SOLzCyG9TKA">Xuất tái từ - 出塞詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%C3%A3-%C4%90%C3%A1i/author-3YuCJNW5VWF3SWDqLImDCQ">Mã Đái</a>)<br></div>	</div>
